What you need to know:

Moussa Sissoko put Mourinho's team ahead in the semi-final at the Tottenham Hotspur StadiumKane fed Tanguy Ndombele and the midfielder's defence-splitting pass teed up Son, who fired high into the roof of the net for his 16th goal of the seasonIt will be the club's first domestic final since losing the 2015 League Cup showpiece against Chelsea